Reasoning: The paper deals with the analysis of ergodic rate in low-resolution ADC systems with transmit antenna selection, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The use of low-resolution ADCs is also relevant to signal processing (cs.SI) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the reduction of power consumption, which is a topic related to computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the simulation results involve the use of multimedia (cs.MM) to validate the derived ergodic rates.
